snippet.title: InEscaped Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Stuck in an abandoned school, you must solve the puzzles to escape while evading a monster lurking to kill you. Solve puzzles, hide, and follow the notes of previous victim to survive. Can you find a way out of the inescapable nightmare of Inescaped?

Buy Now - https://store.steampowered.com/app/2875440/INESCAPED/?beta=0
